headline: 3 Reasons Investors Love Lam Research (LRCX)
summary: The past six months have been a windfall for Lam Research’s shareholders. The company’s stock price has jumped 82.1%, hitting $165.75 per share. This was partly due to its solid quarterly results, and the performance may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
